---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Pediatric Care in Dallas–Fort Worth — Kids &amp; Teens | AymanCare"
  description="Well-child checkups, school physicals, sick visits and vaccinations for children of all ages at four Dallas–Fort Worth clinics."
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
  <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline set:html={"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://aymancare.com/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Services\",\"item\":\"https://aymancare.com/services/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Pediatric Care\",\"item\":\"https://aymancare.com/services/pediatric-care/\"}]}"} />
  </Fragment>
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="breadcrumbs fade-in">
    <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">✦</span><a href="/services/">Services</a><span class="sep">✦</span><span>Pediatric Care</span>
  </div>

  <div class="svc-hero">
    <div>
      <span class="svc-hero-badge fade-in"><span class="ic"></span>Newborn through teen</span>
      <h1 class="page-title fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><em>Pediatric</em><br>care.</h1>
      <p class="svc-hero-lede fade-in">Personalized, child-centered care at every stage of growing up. From newborn well-baby visits to teen health — we meet every child where they are.</p>
      <div class="svc-hero-chips fade-in"><span class="pill">Newborn through teen</span><span class="pill pill-accent">Same-day sick visits</span><span class="pill">School & sports physicals</span></div>
      <div class="svc-hero-ctas fade-in">
        <a href="/book-online/" class="btn btn-primary">Book this visit →</a>
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-outline">Call your nearest clinic</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-hero-visual fade-in">
      <img src="/images/clinic-interior.jpg" alt="Pediatric Care">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" style="padding-top: 0;">
  <div class="svc-main">
    <aside class="svc-aside">
      <div class="aside-card fade-in">
        <div class="l">✦ Service details</div>
        <h3>We care for <em>kids</em></h3>
        <ul><li>Well-child visits</li><li>Immunizations</li><li>Sick visits & same-day care</li><li>Asthma & allergy</li><li>School physicals</li><li>Behavioral screening</li></ul>
      </div>
      <div class="aside-card dark fade-in">
        <div class="l">✦ Ready to book?</div>
        <h3>Same-day <em>appointments</em> available.</h3>
        <a href="/contact/" class="big-num">View all locations →</a>
        <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); font-size: 13px; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;">Call or book online — walk-ins welcome at every location.</p>
        <a href="/book-online/" class="btn btn-accent" style="width: 100%; justify-content: center;">Book online →</a>
      </div>
    </aside>

    <div class="svc-content">
      <h2>Care that <em>listens.</em></h2><p>Kids aren't small adults. Their bodies, minds, and medical needs are uniquely their own — and so is the way they communicate when something feels off. At AymanCare, we take the time to make every child feel comfortable before we ever reach for the stethoscope.</p><h2><em>Well visits</em> & preventive care.</h2><p>From the first newborn visit to every back-to-school check-up, we track growth, development, immunizations, and milestones — catching issues early and answering the questions every parent has but doesn't always know how to ask.</p><blockquote>"Every child deserves a clinic that feels safe. Our job is to make that the default, not the exception."</blockquote><h2><em>When they're sick.</em></h2><p>Same-day appointments and walk-ins are always available for sick kids. Whether it's a stubborn cough, a stomach bug, or an ear infection keeping them up at night, we get them seen, diagnosed, and on the mend.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="svc-grid-band">
  <div class="svc-grid-band-inner">
    <span class="overline fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 16px; display: block;">◆ At a glance</span>
    <h2 class="section-title fade-in" style="font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 48px);">By the <em>numbers.</em></h2>
    <div class="three-col"><div class="mini-card fade-in">
      <div class="num">0 – 17</div>
      <h4>Ages we see</h4>
    </div><div class="mini-card fade-in">
      <div class="num">Same-day</div>
      <h4>Sick visits</h4>
    </div><div class="mini-card fade-in">
      <div class="num">Bilingual</div>
      <h4>Staff support</h4>
    </div></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
<section class="related-services">
      <div class="section-header" style="margin-bottom: 0; padding-bottom: 0; border-bottom: none;">
        <div>
          <span class="overline fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 16px; display: block;">◆ Related services</span>
          <h2 class="section-title fade-in" style="font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 48px);">Explore <em>more</em>.</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="related-grid"><a href="/services/primary-care/" class="related-card fade-in">
          <h4><em>Primary</em> Care</h4>
          <p>Long-term care and annual wellness — your family physician.</p>
          <span class="link">Learn more →</span>
        </a><a href="/services/walk-in-urgent-care/" class="related-card fade-in">
          <h4><em>Walk-In</em> Urgent</h4>
          <p>Same-day care for acute illness, injury, and COVID testing.</p>
          <span class="link">Learn more →</span>
        </a><a href="/services/flu-treatment/" class="related-card fade-in">
          <h4><em>Flu</em> Symptoms</h4>
          <p>Rapid flu diagnosis and treatment.</p>
          <span class="link">Learn more →</span>
        </a></div>
    </section>
</section>

<section class="big-cta">
  <div class="big-cta-inner">
    <span class="overline fade-in">◆ Ready when you are</span>
    <h2 class="fade-in">Let's take care<br>of <em>you.</em></h2>
    <p class="fade-in">Book online in under a minute, or walk into any of our four Dallas-area locations today.</p>
    <div class="cta-row fade-in">
      <a href="/book-online/" class="btn btn-primary">Book appointment →</a>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-outline">Call your nearest clinic</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</Base>
